National Security Advisor Susan E. Rice commends Prime Minister Maliki for supporting Prime Minister-designate Haider al-Abadi in forming a new government in line with the Iraqi constitution. Leaders across the Iraqi political spectrum have expressed their commitment to working with Dr. Abadi to form an inclusive government that addresses the needs and aspirations of the Iraqi people. The international community has also expressed support for the new Prime Minister-designate. These developments are seen as encouraging and the United States remains committed to a strong partnership with Iraq and its people.